        "pf_095b4708_value": "“This is the coldest unit we have ever purchased while living in a mobile home, we have two other units in the bedrooms and they are 8,000btu yet we have to use blackout curtains to shade the sun to still keep the trailer cool.This unit is 12,000btu and AMAZING! set it up and within 10 minutes it was ice cold at 1 pm, the hottest of the day while 84 outside! It maintained 70-71 with no issues until we literally had to turn it back we got so cold! . ”",
