        "pf_5341d6a0_value": "“I purchased the 12,000 BTU 115V so I could install it in my garage without an electrician, it heats and cools very quickly. I bought 12gauge wire to handle 20amp per the manual and wired that into a 20amp outlet plug instead of working directly to the breaker box. since garages in my residential area have standard 20amp breaker it was easy to use 12gauge 20amp wire and a 20amp outlet. ”",
